'''Laneros''' (often stylized as '''LANeros''') is a digital [[community]] of over 370,000 members worldwide, mostly of Hispanic countries, started in 1999.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.laneros.com/foros|title=Forum Statistics|date=2 May 2014|accessdate=2 May 2014}}</ref>  Its slogan is "Digital Addiction".<ref>{{cite web|url=http://primernombre.com/beneficios-web/recomendados/220-bw0017|title=La comunidad mas grande de Colombia|accessdate=2 May 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140506181749/http://primernombre.com/beneficios-web/recomendados/220-bw0017|archivedate=6 May 2014|df=}}</ref>
The name comes from the so-called LAN ([[Local area network]]) parties, which were where the founders gathered to play [[videogames]] 15 years ago, and would translate to English as "LANners".<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.elcolombiano.com/BancoConocimiento/L/laneros_la_comunidad_de_adictos_digitales/laneros_la_comunidad_de_adictos_digitales.asp|editor=[[El Colombiano]]|title=Laneros la comunidad de adictos digitales|accessdate=2 May 2014}}</ref>

